topThird.description: Our application for designers and developers is now closed! As of now, we don't have plans for additional recruitment throughout the school year but make sure to follow us on our social medias for any updates. Thank you for your interest!

middleThird.topDescription: We work with non-profit organizations throughout the school year (September 2020 - June 2021) on a software project that has a meaningful, positive impact and will be a good learning experience for our team.
middleThird.bottomDescription: We have already finalized the projects for the 2020-2021 school year, but if you would like to learn more about our organization or talk about how we can partner together in the future, please email us at committhechange.uci@gmail.com
